<li><a href='http://www.windows7news.com/2011/02/17/microsoft-releases-windows-7-sp1-documentation/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Microsoft Releases Windows 7 SP1 Documentation'>Microsoft Releases Windows 7 SP1 Documentation</a></li>
</ol></p><div class="feedflare">
